authenticate

public ClientLogin.Response authenticate()
                                  throws HttpResponseException,
                                         IOException
Authenticates based on the provided field values.

Throws:
HttpResponseException - if the authentication response has an error code, such as for a CAPTCHA challenge. Call exception.response.parseAs(ClientLoginAuthenticator.ErrorInfo.class) * to parse the response.
IOException - some other kind of I/O exception
